\begin_layout Standard
The zinc hook domain is not structurally separated from the coiled coil
 domain of 
\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout


\backslash
gls{rad}
\end_layout

\end_inset

, i.e., one cannot separate the particular domain just by assessment of the
